{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/ConstructCommunity/awesome-construct/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"29fe37c7-30e3-56e5-a064-572adb103cd4","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-construct-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-construct-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome construct awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome Construct <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge-flat.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.construct.net/\"><img src=\"https://construct-static.com/images/v861/r/global/construct-3-logo_v130.png\" align=\"right\" width=\"100\"></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>You can create the game of your dreams. Build brain tickling puzzles, stunning platformers and immersive RPGs - or break the mould and make something new.\nCreate what you want, how you want with <a href=\"https://www.construct.net\">Construct</a>.</p>\n<p>— <cite>Ashley (Scirra Founder)</cite></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>This list includes all the best tools, tutorials and examples related to the awesome game development engines <a href=\"https://www.scirra.com/construct2\">Construct 2</a> and <a href=\"https://www.construct.net\">Construct</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/armaldio/awesome-construct/blob/master/contributing.md\">How to contribute?</a></p>\n<p align=\"center\">  \n   <img class=\"emoji-icon\" alt=\"emoji-sparkles\" data-icon=\"emoji-sparkles\" style=\"display: inline; margin: 0; margin-top: 1px; position: relative; top: 5px; width: 25px\" src=\"data:image/png;base64, \" title=\"emoji-sparkles\" /> <a href=\"https://github.com/WebCreationClub/awesome-construct/blob/master/c2vsc3.md\">Compare Construct 2 and Construct 3</a>  <img class=\"emoji-icon\" alt=\"emoji-sparkles\" data-icon=\"emoji-sparkles\" style=\"display: inline; margin: 0; margin-top: 1px; position: relative; top: 5px; width: 25px\" src=\"data:image/png;base64, \" title=\"emoji-sparkles\" />\n</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#community\">Community</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#games-showcase\">Games Showcase</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#hosting\">Hosting</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tools\">Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#export\">Export</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#pluginsbehaviorseffects\">Plugins/Behaviors/Effects</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tutorials\">Tutorials</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#e-books\">E-Books</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#useful-links\">Useful Links</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"community\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#community\" aria-label=\"community permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Community</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://discord.gg/8RJBHbX\">Discord Server</a> - <a href=\"https://www.construct.net/forum/construct-2/general-discussion-17/there-is-a-construct-2-discord-117214\">Scirra Forum Thread</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.construct.net/forum/construct-2/how-do-i-18/how-do-i-frequently-asked-ques-41236\">FAQ</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.construct.net/forum\">Forums</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/construct-2\">Stack Overflow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/construct/\">Reddit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/constructteam\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ConstructTeam/\">Facebook</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"games-showcase\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#games-showcase\" aria-label=\"games showcase permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Games Showcase</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=103535227\">Games on Steam</a> - List of Steam games made with the engine.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://itch.io/games/tag-construct-2\">Games on itch.io</a> - List of itch.io games made with the engine.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.madewithconstruct.com/\">Games made with Construct</a> - A website that list all the games made with the engine.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"hosting\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hosting\" aria-label=\"hosting permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hosting</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.itch.io\">itch.io</a> - Platform where to host, showcase, promote or sell your games - <strong>Free</strong>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://pages.github.com\">GitHub Pages</a> - Platform where to host an exported game as a static website - <strong>Free</strong>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://surge.sh/\">Surge</a> - Platform where to host an exported game as a static website - <strong>Free/Paid</strong>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zeit.co/now\">Now</a> - Platform where to host an exported game as a static website, a docker image or a Node.js server - <strong>Free/Paid</strong>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.netlify.com/\">Netlify</a> - Platform where to host an exported game as a static website - <strong>Free/Paid</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tools\" aria-label=\"tools permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tools</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://rexrainbow.github.io/C2RexDoc/c2rexplugins.weebly.com/index.html\">Rex's Plugins Tool</a> - The personnal addon manager of Rex.Rainbow.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"export\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#export\" aria-label=\"export permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Export</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://electronforconstruct.armaldio.xyz\">ElectronForConstruct</a> - Export your games using Electron instead of NW.js.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://mp2.dk/chowdren/\">Chowdren</a> - Blazingly fast runtime for Clickteam Fusion and Scirra Construct.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"pluginsbehaviorseffects\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#pluginsbehaviorseffects\" aria-label=\"pluginsbehaviorseffects permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Plugins/Behaviors/Effects</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.construct.net/forum/extending-construct-2/addons-29/c2-plugins-and-behaviors-list-42712\">[Kyatric] C2 Plugins and Behaviors List</a> - Complete list of Plugins and Behaviours available on the forums.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.construct.net/forum/extending-construct-2/effects-31/webgl-effects-list-51897\">[Kyatric] WebGL Effects List</a> - Complete list of Effects available on the forums.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"tutorials\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tutorials\" aria-label=\"tutorials permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tutorials</h2>\n<h3 id=\"youtube\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#youtube\" aria-label=\"youtube permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>YouTube</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLmyh0_jcCzcoPTgHkm4CJSw_sdK5lPSb_\">[ArcadEdGames] Construct 2 Tutorials</a> - YouTube channel about making all sort of stuff.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/ScirraVideos/playlists\">[ScirraVideos] Construct 2 Tutorials</a> - Official Scirra's YouTube channel.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGdBDrsyOPm9XGiq1w_8DvbEQbHmkn7fx\">[C2Tuts 2D Game Development] Construct 2 Tutorials</a> - General tutorials.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLsJBMeqEdtggBJBiuX8bnF10ewHjdE20e\">[Nicholas Dingle] Construct 2 Tutorials</a> - Number of tutorials covering different games you can create and different tricks.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLq6aUvz66jtfnuyOKnPXO5dZly6CB8naA\">[John Maksym] Construct 2 Tutorial Series</a> - General tutorials.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLxwakQrJudt_NQlMp6oVuBdB-WIDKgoQ3\">[ConstructG] Create Simple Platformer Game With Construct 2</a> - Tutorial about how to make a platformer game.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/kanedarkon/videos?view=0&#x26;flow=grid&#x26;sort=da\">[Diego Lizarazo] Construct 2 Tutorials</a> - Random stuff.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLusL6SZZRaWr4zqm6GrQHmOuShwtypRJ5\">[English Acorn] Construct 2 - Tutorials</a> - General tutorials about the editor interface.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLusL6SZZRaWqP6UmVPs9Ml8BRo2t-wvnT\">[English Acorn] Construct 2 - Plugins and Objects</a> - Tutorials about plugins and how they work inside the Editor.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCR955dujboBxEN2VJlZwJw/playlists\">[Game Development] Construct 2 - Tutorials</a> - General tutorials.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6gx4Cwl9DGAfHxsK6bji7trLS-N0nKF-\">[thenewboston] Game Development w/ Construct 2 Playlist</a> - The official playlist for thenewboston Game Development.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6gx4Cwl9DGAp287UuTE0-K7Ty-b8rGAX\">[thenewboston] Platform Game Development w/ Construct 2 Playlist</a> - Official playlist for thenewboston Platform Game Development.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6gx4Cwl9DGDexNbWi0uPBP6buduUZO3Q\">[thenewboston] Physics Puzzle Game Development w/ Construct 2 Playlist</a> - The official playlist for thenewboston Physics Puzzle Game Development Tutorials.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLz66pfeeD4TcPN9kO7JlqiITpgi_WWgn7\">[LividProductions] Platformer Tutorials</a> - This series will teach you how to make a platformer.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQkYeiHm9URZsa7nugUg1lw/playlists\">[Jerementor] Construct 2 Tutorials</a> - General tutorials.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLdn9X5UVD8H1dEcWVjYU9E5fbpPGjZnQv\">[Kawaerri] Scirra Construct 2 Tutorial</a> - General tutorials.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXIcG5r9W_Iw6dui35g9oLQ/playlists\">[Gamer Z] - Tutorial List</a> - General tutorials.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLO3K3VFvlU6B1InGyrx7Iz7w_MDizWlXK\">[TodaysTuts] Construct 2 - Behaviors</a> - Tutorials about Behaviours.</li>\n<li>Let's Make Games: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cvItNHEMB80\">[PONG]</a> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nYULTk2BpKY\">[ASTEROIDS]</a> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eBccn1qMB_U\">[Flappy Bird]</a> - Tutorials on how to make specifi games.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL59F92017DA9887DB\">Construct 2 Tutorials - Breakout Clone</a> - Learn how to create a Brakeout game.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"other-sources\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#other-sources\" aria-label=\"other sources permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Other Sources</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://mva.microsoft.com/en-US/training-courses/game-development-with-construct-2-8355\">[MVA] Game Development with Construct 2 (Basic)</a> - Basic course about making games.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mva.microsoft.com/en-US/training-courses/developing-windows-10-games-with-construct-2-16335\">[MVA] Developing Windows 10 Games with Construct 2 (Advanced)</a> - Advanced course about making games.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.udemy.com/learn-construct-2-creating-a-pixel-platformer-in-html5/\">[Udemy FREE!] Learn Construct 2</a> - Creating a Pixel Platformer in HTML5.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gamedevelopment.tutsplus.com/categories/construct-2\">[TutPlus] Construct 2 Tutorials</a> - General tutorials.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"e-books\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#e-books\" aria-label=\"e books permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>E-Books</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.construct.net/blogs/construct-official-blog-1/level-zero-free-construct-2-book-853\">Level Zero</a> - Complete book on how to make games.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"useful-links\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#useful-links\" aria-label=\"useful links permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1